headline: TSLA Q1 Earnings Preview: Can Energy Storage Offset Weak EV Sales?
summary: Energy storage is Tesla's fastest-growing unit but makes up just over 12% of revenues, too little to offset weakness in the core auto business (~75% of revenues).
